In the individual trading divisions the improvement was most significant in
property and investment, where there was a profit of Pounds 1.67m before
interest and tax, compared to a loss of Pounds 5.56m).
SHT's property division has a mixed portfolio of land around Britain and
owns tenement flats in the Glasgow area.
