from Copenhagen.
But the government will waive payment of the tax for the fourth quarter of
1991, which falls due on April 20. The labour market tax has yielded about
Kr55bn (Pounds 5bn) since 1987, a sum equal to more than 6 per cent of 1991
GDP.
